platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Game 16. Help these critters get back home!

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Typically when you love something, you dont tear it up. But in this Apple Design Award winner, youll need to rip and rearrange each stage to help your lil alien buddies reach their spaceship. The design is superb, the music is wonderful. But hands-down the best thing about this puzzler? It feels totally original.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Slice apart stages and help cute creatures find safety.
